== How to enter into bootloader (fastboot) ==
* Shutdown the phone completely.
* Press {{Button|Volume Down}} and {{Button|Power}} button simultaneously to enter fastboot mode.

== How to enter into recovery mode ==

* Shutdown the phone completely
* Press {{Button|Volume Up}} and {{Button|Power}} button simultaneously to enter the recovery (MI or Custom).

== Forked kernel ==

